  • Field Details

    • id

      private Long id
      The unique identifier for the notification. Generated automatically.

    • type

      private NotificationType type
      The type of notification. Stored as a string representation of the `NotificationType` enum.

    • content

      private String content
      The content of the notification. Must always be sent and can be updated.

    • creationDate

      private LocalDateTime creationDate
      The date and time when the notification was created. Cannot be updated once set.

    • notificationIsRead

      private Boolean notificationIsRead
      Indicates whether the notification has been read and clicked by the user. Can be updated.

    • notificationIsSeen

      private Boolean notificationIsSeen
      Is seen indicates a notifications which content has been seen by the user. This is different from read, as it indicates that the user has viewed the notification content. Can be updated.

    • messageCount

      private Integer messageCount
      The number of associated messages. Must always be sent and can be updated.

    • emailSent

      private Boolean emailSent
      The number of associated messages. Must always be sent and can be updated.

    • user

      private UserEntity user
      The user associated with the notification. Many-to-one relationship with `UserEntity`.

    • sender

      private UserEntity sender
      The sender of the notification. Many-to-one relationship with `UserEntity`.
